Getting and Playing Games
=========================

There are two games for Solarus.
The Legend of Zelda: Mystery of Solarus DX (zsdx)
and
The Legend of Zelda: Mystery of Solarus DX (zsxd)

To download the games, go to:
http://www.zelda-solarus.com/downloads/zsdx/ (or zsxd/)
and download zsdx-${V}.tar.gz, where ${V} is 1.6 or higher.
Earlier versions will not work with this version of Solarus.

Extract the tarball to the directory of your choice, and run solarus
in the extracted directory.
